      • getMatchedDay

        public List<OperationalTime.EscalationTime> getMatchedDay(int currentDay)
        Gets the escalation time for the current day.
        It's usefully for the time ranges ( see ITime#DAY_MON_FRI ).
        E.g. if the current day is Monday and the escalation time is defined as day range( ITime#DAY_MON_FRI ) the day range is returned because the day range contains the current day.
        Parameters:
        currentDay -
        Returns:
        the escalation time object for the current day
